{
  "stem": "8610.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was most upset.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knew Bernstein very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't give a reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they felt it was-- it would militate against good relations with Germans after the war. 40 years after the liberation, I had a brain wave.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I organized a reunion of ministry personnel who had any connection with Belsen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wrote to the national press up and down the country-- and local press, hundreds and hundreds of newspapers-- saying that I was going to hold a reunion of anybody who had any military connection with Belsen.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And several hundred men came down to London, spent the day with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Lord Bernstein put his film at my disposal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was the first time it was shown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he introduced it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was then 80-odd years of age.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as he spoke about it, that poor man broke down into tears.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a moving occasion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, this is a film I wanted to show.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it's taken 40 years for it to be shown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then later on it appeared on Radio 4.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And well, that was the situation-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] certain reluctance to revive these memories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, I think Spielberg's doing a good thing in keeping the archives going.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because those of us who have personal memories, we are getting older.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We won't have much longer to live.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so here we are, telling the story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wrote this little book called which appeared some six months or so ago.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, I was-- I was one of those people who felt reluctant to put it on, to write about it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'd written about my experiences in the Middle East.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow I was reluctant to put it on print.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
